          "text": "The complexity level of this stored procedure is considered medium. It involves multiple input parameters, a conditional check to prevent duplicate entries, and an insertion operation based on a selection from another table. The logic is straightforward but requires understanding of the relationships between tables and the purpose of each parameter."
